The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , June 22 , 2008                
	Metro station    Attend a programme to celebrate the renaming of Sovabazar Metro station to Sovabazar-Sutanuti station, 10.30am.        
	Dementia    Listen to a talk on dementia at Saturday Club, 11am to 1pm.        
	Dance    Watch a dance programme at Gyan Manch, 6.30pm.        
	Cultural    Enjoy a cultural programme at Bangla Akademi, 5pm.        
	Anniversary    Be there at the 98th birth anniversary celebrations of Ustad Mustak Ali Khan at Umak Bhavan, 6E Uma Kanta Sen Lane, 6pm.        
	Furniture    Check out Walias Furniture Show at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.         
	Eye on Art    Browse through an exhibition of contemporary paintings at Academy of Fine Arts, New South (B) Gallery, 3pm to 8pm.				 																																	  Drop in at Different Strokes, an exhibition of paintings by Shyamal Sen and Chhanda Singh, at Gallery 79, 4pm to 7pm.			 																																	   Stop over at Art on Display, an exhibition of sculptures by Soumen Das and pattachitra by Bijay Parida, at Starmark, South City Mall, 11am to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                              
